.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, eggplant, kale, peas
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, drawing, woodworking
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, indian, mexican, spanish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, animation, documentary, satire
 1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an even position##4
 2. the indian is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 4. the person eating eggplant is the colombian##1
 5. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 6. the colombian is on the left or right of the mexican##3
 7. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 8. the spanish is on the left or right of the person watching time-travel movies##3
 9. the mexican is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating kale is in an odd position##4
11. the mexican is the person who's hobby is drawing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | carrot  | eggplant    | kale     | peas       |
| Hobby         | drawing | woodworking | baking   | collecting |
| Nationality   | mexican | colombian   | indian   | spanish    |
| Movie-Genre         | documentary | satire  | time-travel | animation   |

