.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, iced-tea, sprite, water
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, balloon-flower, amaryllis, marigold
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, sudoku, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, parkour, surfing
 1. the person drinking fanta is the person who growsbegonia##1
 2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 3. the person who growsbegonia is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 4. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
 5. the person drinking iced-tea is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
 7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is the person who's hobby is chess##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
11. the person drinking sprite is the person who growsmarigold##1
12. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person who growsbegonia##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | water       | sprite   | fanta   | iced-tea   |
| Flower       | balloon-flower        | marigold | begonia    | amaryllis       |
| Hobby      | woodworking | chess    | sudoku  | card-games |
| Sport      | ice-hockey  | parkour  | cycling | surfing    |

