 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
 5. the bolivar-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 6. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person eating potato##1
 7. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
