.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, hot-chocolate, juice, milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, singing, video-games
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, december, november, february
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, sailing, volleyball, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
11. the person who's birthday is in february is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Beverage      | juice       | hot-chocolate | 7up        | milk        |
| Hobby         | video-games | singing       | card-games | photography |
| Birthday   | february     | december        | may    | november      |
| Sport         | sailing     | volleyball    | water-polo | badminton   |

